  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary efficacy objective of this clinical investigation is to demonstrate that the
      Ventricular Intrinsic Preference (VIP™) feature allows to reduce the medium- and long-term
      incidence of unnecessary ventricular pacing in patients with intact AV conduction.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
